  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sky End Market” is a supermarket management game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sell your products to cute customers, animals, and robots drawn with pixel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308550/extras/99e02c6216a25649b40e68574a770ff0.avif?t=1771043999\" width=610 height=143 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your store</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your own supermarket by freely setting up shelves, checkout counters, shopping baskets, decorations, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Display</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new products, stock them and put them on the shelves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cashier</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the cash register, scan items and receive payment. Enjoy a variety of payment formats, including cash, cashless codes handled by robots, and acorns handled by animals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308550/extras/b4d07c595eb3a62eef3bdddf4cb841cc.avif?t=1771043999\" width=610 height=148 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The future just before human extinction</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a time just before the extinction of the human race. It is the last place on earth where survivors, robots, and animals are huddled together for the last time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will help them by managing the world's last supermarket.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the development</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The exciting feeling you had as a child when you played shop with money made out of paper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I want to express that in a 2D world of cute dots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >That's why I'm making this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is made entirely by one developer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only one person, but I will update frequently and do my best !!!!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please support me !!!!!!!!!!!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sky End Market” is a supermarket management game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sell your products to cute customers, animals, and robots drawn with pixel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308550/extras/99e02c6216a25649b40e68574a770ff0.avif?t=1771043999\" width=610 height=143 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your store</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your own supermarket by freely setting up shelves, checkout counters, shopping baskets, decorations, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Display</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new products, stock them and put them on the shelves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cashier</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the cash register, scan items and receive payment. Enjoy a variety of payment formats, including cash, cashless codes handled by robots, and acorns handled by animals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308550/extras/b4d07c595eb3a62eef3bdddf4cb841cc.avif?t=1771043999\" width=610 height=148 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The future just before human extinction</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a time just before the extinction of the human race. It is the last place on earth where survivors, robots, and animals are huddled together for the last time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will help them by managing the world's last supermarket.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the development</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The exciting feeling you had as a child when you played shop with money made out of paper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I want to express that in a 2D world of cute dots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >That's why I'm making this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is made entirely by one developer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only one person, but I will update frequently and do my best !!!!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please support me !!!!!!!!!!!</p>",
